snippet.title: Side Pocket 3 -Sega Saturn - Intro and Gameplay
snippet.description: Really nice looking and playing Pool game, with some great 3D polygons and great ball physics, the soundtrack is awesome too.  One also takes it, the Team were massive fans of Resident Evil/BioHazard LOL
